{
  "video_id": "Sf8j5LFv3nI",
  "title": "In praise of conflict | Jonathan Marks",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12460.0,
      "end_time": 13916.0,
      "text": "Twenty years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13940.0,
      "end_time": 16875.0,
      "text": "when I was a barrister and human rights lawyer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16900.0,
      "end_time": 19875.0,
      "text": "in full-time legal practice in London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19900.0,
      "end_time": 22760.0,
      "text": "and the highest court in the land"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22100.0,
      "end_time": 26516.0,
      "text": "still convened, some would say by an accident of history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26540.0,
      "end_time": 27860.0,
      "text": "in this building here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28660.0,
      "end_time": 31716.0,
      "text": "I met a young man who had just quit his job"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31740.0,
      "end_time": 33169.0,
      "text": "in the British Foreign Office."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33740.0,
      "end_time": 36360.0,
      "text": "When I asked him, \"Why did you leave,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36600.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "he told me this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38340.0,
      "end_time": 41360.0,
      "text": "He had gone to his boss one morning and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41600.0,
      "end_time": 45180.0,
      "text": "\"Let&#39;s do something about human rights abuses in China.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46200.0,
      "end_time": 47996.0,
      "text": "And his boss had replied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48200.0,
      "end_time": 50716.0,
      "text": "\"We can&#39;t do anything about human rights abuses in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50740.0,
      "end_time": 53340.0,
      "text": "because we have trade relations with China.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54500.0,
      "end_time": 57760.0,
      "text": "So my friend went away with his tail between his legs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57100.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "and six months later, he returned again to his boss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61600.0,
      "end_time": 62676.0,
      "text": "and he said this time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62700.0,
      "end_time": 66196.0,
      "text": "\"Let&#39;s do something about human rights in Burma,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66220.0,
      "end_time": 67420.0,
      "text": "as it was then called."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68220.0,
      "end_time": 70356.0,
      "text": "His boss once again paused"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70380.0,
      "end_time": 74396.0,
      "text": "and said, \"Oh, but we can&#39;t do anything about human rights in Burma"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74420.0,
      "end_time": 78760.0,
      "text": "because we don&#39;t have any trade relations with Burma.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78100.0,
      "end_time": 79756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79780.0,
      "end_time": 81876.0,
      "text": "This was the moment he knew he had to leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81900.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t just the hypocrisy that got to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84980.0,
      "end_time": 88236.0,
      "text": "It was the unwillingness of his government"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90876.0,
      "text": "to engage in conflict with other governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90900.0,
      "end_time": 92676.0,
      "text": "in tense discussions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92700.0,
      "end_time": 96500.0,
      "text": "all the while, innocent people were being harmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97420.0,
      "end_time": 99956.0,
      "text": "We are constantly told"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99980.0,
      "end_time": 102600.0,
      "text": "that conflict is bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102740.0,
      "end_time": 104780.0,
      "text": "that compromise is good;"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105460.0,
      "end_time": 107116.0,
      "text": "that conflict is bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107140.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "but consensus is good;"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109940.0,
      "end_time": 112155.0,
      "text": "that conflict is bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112180.0,
      "end_time": 114740.0,
      "text": "and collaboration is good."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115860.0,
      "end_time": 117156.0,
      "text": "But in my view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117180.0,
      "end_time": 119556.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s far too simple a vision of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119580.0,
      "end_time": 121476.0,
      "text": "We cannot know"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121500.0,
      "end_time": 123556.0,
      "text": "whether conflict is bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123580.0,
      "end_time": 126396.0,
      "text": "unless we know who is fighting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126420.0,
      "end_time": 128556.0,
      "text": "why they are fighting"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128580.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130436.00000000001,
      "text": "and how they are fighting."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130460.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133916.0,
      "text": "And compromises can be thoroughly rotten"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133940.0,
      "end_time": 136620.0,
      "text": "if they harm people who are not at the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137420.0,
      "end_time": 139834.0,
      "text": "people who are vulnerable, disempowered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139859.0,
      "end_time": 143140.0,
      "text": "people whom we have an obligation to protect."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144300.0,
      "end_time": 147356.0,
      "text": "Now, you might be somewhat skeptical of a lawyer"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147380.0,
      "end_time": 150555.0,
      "text": "arguing about the benefits of conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150580.0,
      "end_time": 153196.0,
      "text": "and creating problems for compromise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153220.0,
      "end_time": 155360.0,
      "text": "but I did also qualify as a mediator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155600.0,
      "end_time": 158340.0,
      "text": "and these days, I spend my time giving talks about ethics for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158980.0,
      "end_time": 162600.0,
      "text": "So as my bank manager likes to remind me, I&#39;m downwardly mobile."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164100.0,
      "end_time": 167116.0,
      "text": "But if you accept my argument,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167140.0,
      "end_time": 170315.0,
      "text": "it should change not just the way we lead our personal lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170340.0,
      "end_time": 172660.0,
      "text": "which I wish to put to one side for the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173420.0,
      "end_time": 177196.0,
      "text": "but it will change the way we think about major problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 177220.0,
      "end_time": 179980.0,
      "text": "of public health and the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 182459.0,
      "text": "Let me explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184180.0,
      "end_time": 186556.0,
      "text": "Every middle schooler in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186580.0,
      "end_time": 189236.0,
      "text": "my 12-year-old daughter included,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 193116.0,
      "text": "learns that there are three branches of government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193140.0,
      "end_time": 196980.0,
      "text": "the legislative, the executive and the judicial branch."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197660.0,
      "end_time": 199760.0,
      "text": "James Madison wrote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199100.0,
      "end_time": 204116.0,
      "text": "\"If there is any principle more sacred in our Constitution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204140.0,
      "end_time": 206875.0,
      "text": "and indeed in any free constitution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206900.0,
      "end_time": 208396.0,
      "text": "than any other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208420.0,
      "end_time": 210916.0,
      "text": "it is that which separates"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 210940.0,
      "end_time": 215600.0,
      "text": "the legislative, the executive and the judicial powers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215900.0,
      "end_time": 219156.0,
      "text": "Now, the framers were not just concerned"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219180.0,
      "end_time": 223276.0,
      "text": "about the concentration and exercise of power."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 223300.0,
      "end_time": 227300.0,
      "text": "They also understood the perils of influence."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 233356.0,
      "text": "Judges cannot determine the constitutionality of laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 233380.0,
      "end_time": 237156.0,
      "text": "if they participate in making those laws,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237180.0,
      "end_time": 241116.0,
      "text": "nor can they hold the other branches of government accountable"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 241140.0,
      "end_time": 243760.0,
      "text": "if they collaborate with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 243100.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "or enter into close relationships with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247300.0,
      "end_time": 251196.0,
      "text": "The Constitution is, as one famous scholar put it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251220.0,
      "end_time": 253460.0,
      "text": "\"an invitation to struggle.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254600.0,
      "end_time": 256836.0,
      "text": "And we the people are served"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256860.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "when those branches do, indeed, struggle with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 263100.0,
      "end_time": 266676.0,
      "text": "Now, we recognize the importance of struggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 266700.0,
      "end_time": 269596.0,
      "text": "not just in the public sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 269620.0,
      "end_time": 271996.0,
      "text": "between our branches of government."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 272200.0,
      "end_time": 275356.0,
      "text": "We also know it too in the private sector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 275380.0,
      "end_time": 277980.0,
      "text": "in relationships among corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 279180.0,
      "end_time": 284196.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s imagine that two American airlines get together and agree"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 284220.0,
      "end_time": 286396.0,
      "text": "that they will not drop the price"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286420.0,
      "end_time": 290780.0,
      "text": "of their economy class airfares below 250 dollars a ticket."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291420.0,
      "end_time": 295276.0,
      "text": "That is collaboration, some would say collusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 295300.0,
      "end_time": 296636.0,
      "text": "not competition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 296660.0,
      "end_time": 299476.0,
      "text": "and we the people are harmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 299500.0,
      "end_time": 301340.0,
      "text": "because we pay more for our tickets."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 302660.0,
      "end_time": 304916.0,
      "text": "Imagine similarly two airlines were to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 304940.0,
      "end_time": 309956.0,
      "text": "\"Look, Airline A, we&#39;ll take the route from LA to Chicago,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 309980.0,
      "end_time": 313156.0,
      "text": "and Airline B says, \"We&#39;ll take the route from Chicago to DC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313180.0,
      "end_time": 314636.0,
      "text": "and we won&#39;t compete.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 314660.0,
      "end_time": 319276.0,
      "text": "Once again, that&#39;s collaboration or collusion instead of competition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319300.0,
      "end_time": 322200.0,
      "text": "and we the people are harmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 323700.0,
      "end_time": 329156.0,
      "text": "So we understand the importance of struggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 329180.0,
      "end_time": 333420.0,
      "text": "when it comes to relationships between branches of government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 334900.0,
      "end_time": 336596.0,
      "text": "the public sector."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 336620.0,
      "end_time": 340360.0,
      "text": "We also understand the importance of conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 340600.0,
      "end_time": 344396.0,
      "text": "when it comes to relationships among corporations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 344420.0,
      "end_time": 346760.0,
      "text": "the private sector."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346100.0,
      "end_time": 348676.0,
      "text": "But where we have forgotten it"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348700.0,
      "end_time": 353116.0,
      "text": "is in the relationships between the public and the private."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 353140.0,
      "end_time": 356836.0,
      "text": "And governments all over the world are collaborating with industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 356860.0,
      "end_time": 360636.0,
      "text": "to solve problems of public health and the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360660.0,
      "end_time": 363636.0,
      "text": "often collaborating with the very corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 363660.0,
      "end_time": 369500.0,
      "text": "that are creating or exacerbating the problems they are trying to solve."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 370900.0,
      "end_time": 374476.0,
      "text": "We are told that these relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 374500.0,
      "end_time": 376180.0,
      "text": "are a win-win."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377180.0,
      "end_time": 380340.0,
      "text": "But what if someone is losing out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 382100.0,
      "end_time": 384420.0,
      "text": "Let me give you some examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385660.0,
      "end_time": 389156.0,
      "text": "A United Nations agency decided to address a serious problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 389180.0,
      "end_time": 392780.0,
      "text": "poor sanitation in schools in rural India."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 394200.0,
      "end_time": 398750.0,
      "text": "They did so not just in collaboration with national and local governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 398100.0,
      "end_time": 400596.0,
      "text": "but also with a television company"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 400620.0,
      "end_time": 404460.0,
      "text": "and with a major multinational soda company."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 405460.0,
      "end_time": 408596.0,
      "text": "In exchange for less than one million dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 408620.0,
      "end_time": 412996.0,
      "text": "that corporation received the benefits of a months-long promotional campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 413200.0,
      "end_time": 415195.0,
      "text": "including a 12-hour telethon"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 415220.0,
      "end_time": 418420.0,
      "text": "all using the company&#39;s logo and color scheme."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419860.0,
      "end_time": 421380.0,
      "text": "This was an arrangement"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421980.0,
      "end_time": 424836.0,
      "text": "which was totally understandable"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 424860.0,
      "end_time": 426796.0,
      "text": "from the corporation&#39;s point of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 426820.0,
      "end_time": 429356.0,
      "text": "It enhances the reputation of the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 429380.0,
      "end_time": 431900.0,
      "text": "and it creates brand loyalty for its products."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 433180.0,
      "end_time": 434796.0,
      "text": "But in my view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 434820.0,
      "end_time": 438516.0,
      "text": "this is profoundly problematic for the intergovernmental agency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 438540.0,
      "end_time": 442700.0,
      "text": "an agency that has a mission to promote sustainable living."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 443700.0,
      "end_time": 446836.0,
      "text": "By increasing consumption of sugar-sweetened beverages"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 446860.0,
      "end_time": 451156.0,
      "text": "made from scarce local water supplies and drunk out of plastic bottles"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 451180.0,
      "end_time": 454196.0,
      "text": "in a country that is already grappling with obesity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 454220.0,
      "end_time": 457636.0,
      "text": "this is neither sustainable from a public health"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 457660.0,
      "end_time": 460556.0,
      "text": "nor an environmental point of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 460580.0,
      "end_time": 463916.0,
      "text": "And in order to solve one public health problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 463940.0,
      "end_time": 466236.0,
      "text": "the agency is sowing the seeds"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 467460.0,
      "text": "of another."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 469300.0,
      "end_time": 473596.0,
      "text": "This is just one example of dozens I discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 473620.0,
      "end_time": 478716.0,
      "text": "in researching a book on the relationships between government and industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 478740.0,
      "end_time": 482516.0,
      "text": "I could also have told you about the initiatives in parks"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 482540.0,
      "end_time": 484156.0,
      "text": "in London and throughout Britain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 484180.0,
      "end_time": 486580.0,
      "text": "involving the same company, promoting exercise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 487380.0,
      "end_time": 492236.0,
      "text": "or indeed of the British government creating voluntary pledges"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 494436.0,
      "text": "in partnership with industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 494460.0,
      "end_time": 497195.0,
      "text": "instead of regulating industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 497220.0,
      "end_time": 502876.0,
      "text": "These collaborations or partnerships have become the paradigm in public health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 502900.0,
      "end_time": 506955.0,
      "text": "and once again, they make sense from the point of view of industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 506980.0,
      "end_time": 510596.0,
      "text": "It allows them to frame public health problems and their solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 510620.0,
      "end_time": 512756.0,
      "text": "in ways that are least threatening to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 512780.0,
      "end_time": 515635.0,
      "text": "most consonant with their commercial interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 515659.0,
      "end_time": 518236.0,
      "text": "So obesity becomes a problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 518260.0,
      "end_time": 522515.0,
      "text": "of individual decision-making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 522539.0,
      "end_time": 524594.0,
      "text": "of personal behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 524619.0,
      "end_time": 527796.0,
      "text": "personal responsibility and lack of physical activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 527820.0,
      "end_time": 529916.0,
      "text": "It is not a problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 529940.0,
      "end_time": 531355.0,
      "text": "when framed this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 531379.0,
      "end_time": 534996.0,
      "text": "of a multinational food system involving major corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 535200.0,
      "end_time": 536675.0,
      "text": "And again, I don&#39;t blame industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 536700.0,
      "end_time": 540116.0,
      "text": "Industry naturally engages in strategies of influence"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 540140.0,
      "end_time": 542620.0,
      "text": "to promote its commercial interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 543380.0,
      "end_time": 546636.0,
      "text": "But governments have a responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 546660.0,
      "end_time": 548716.0,
      "text": "to develop counterstrategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 548740.0,
      "end_time": 550556.0,
      "text": "to protect us"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 550580.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "and the common good."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 553980.0,
      "end_time": 557540.0,
      "text": "The mistake that governments are making"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 558300.0,
      "end_time": 560876.0,
      "text": "when they collaborate in this way"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 560900.0,
      "end_time": 562236.0,
      "text": "with industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 564836.0,
      "text": "is that they conflate"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 564860.0,
      "end_time": 566676.0,
      "text": "the common good"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 566700.0,
      "end_time": 567900.0,
      "text": "with common ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 568900.0,
      "end_time": 571675.0,
      "text": "When you collaborate with industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 571700.0,
      "end_time": 574516.0,
      "text": "you necessarily put off the table"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 574540.0,
      "end_time": 578116.0,
      "text": "things that might promote the common good to which industry will not agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 578140.0,
      "end_time": 580915.0,
      "text": "Industry will not agree to increased regulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 580940.0,
      "end_time": 585116.0,
      "text": "unless it believes this will stave off even more regulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 585140.0,
      "end_time": 588380.0,
      "text": "or perhaps knock some competitors out of the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 589780.0,
      "end_time": 592760.0,
      "text": "Nor can companies agree to do certain things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 592100.0,
      "end_time": 595760.0,
      "text": "for example raise the prices of their unhealthy products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 595100.0,
      "end_time": 597236.0,
      "text": "because that would violate competition law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 598460.0,
      "text": "as we&#39;ve established."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 600380.0,
      "end_time": 603596.0,
      "text": "So our governments should not confound"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 603620.0,
      "end_time": 606760.0,
      "text": "the common good and common ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 606100.0,
      "end_time": 611340.0,
      "text": "especially when common ground means reaching agreement with industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612340.0,
      "end_time": 614360.0,
      "text": "I want to give you another example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 614600.0,
      "end_time": 616195.0,
      "text": "moving from high-profile collaboration"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 616220.0,
      "end_time": 618716.0,
      "text": "to something that is below ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 618740.0,
      "end_time": 621996.0,
      "text": "both literally and figuratively:"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 622200.0,
      "end_time": 624620.0,
      "text": "the hydraulic fracturing of natural gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 625140.0,
      "end_time": 628836.0,
      "text": "Imagine that you purchase a plot of land"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 628860.0,
      "end_time": 631760.0,
      "text": "not knowing the mineral rights have been sold."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 631100.0,
      "end_time": 632900.0,
      "text": "This is before the fracking boom."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 634180.0,
      "end_time": 637195.0,
      "text": "You build your dream home on that plot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 637220.0,
      "end_time": 638836.0,
      "text": "and shortly afterwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 638860.0,
      "end_time": 644260.0,
      "text": "you discover that a gas company is building a well pad on your land."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 644860.0,
      "end_time": 648260.0,
      "text": "That was the plight of the Hallowich family."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 649200.0,
      "end_time": 651836.0,
      "text": "Within a very short period of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 651860.0,
      "end_time": 655760.0,
      "text": "they began to complain of headaches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 655100.0,
      "end_time": 658316.0,
      "text": "of sore throats, of itchy eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 658340.0,
      "end_time": 661156.0,
      "text": "in addition to the interference of the noise, vibration"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 661180.0,
      "end_time": 664315.0,
      "text": "and the bright lights from the flaring of natural gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 664340.0,
      "end_time": 666660.0,
      "text": "They were very vocal in their criticisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 667780.0,
      "end_time": 669140.0,
      "text": "and then they fell silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 670220.0,
      "end_time": 673476.0,
      "text": "And thanks to the Pittsburgh Post-Gazette, where this image appeared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 673500.0,
      "end_time": 676356.0,
      "text": "and one other newspaper, we discovered why they fell silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 676380.0,
      "end_time": 680760.0,
      "text": "The newspapers went to the court and said, \"What happened to the Hallowiches?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 680100.0,
      "end_time": 683476.0,
      "text": "And it turned out the Hallowiches had made a secret settlement"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 683500.0,
      "end_time": 687396.0,
      "text": "with the gas operators, and it was a take-it-or-leave-it settlement."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 687420.0,
      "end_time": 688675.0,
      "text": "The gas company said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 688700.0,
      "end_time": 691116.0,
      "text": "you can have a six-figure sum"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 691140.0,
      "end_time": 693276.0,
      "text": "to move elsewhere and start your lives again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 693300.0,
      "end_time": 694516.0,
      "text": "but in return"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 694540.0,
      "end_time": 698396.0,
      "text": "you must promise not to speak of your experience with our company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 698420.0,
      "end_time": 700996.0,
      "text": "not to speak of your experience with fracking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 701200.0,
      "end_time": 704740.0,
      "text": "not to speak about the health consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 705500.0,
      "end_time": 708420.0,
      "text": "that might have been revealed by a medical examination."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 709540.0,
      "end_time": 712356.0,
      "text": "Now, I do not blame the Hallowiches for accepting"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 712380.0,
      "end_time": 715196.0,
      "text": "a take-it-or-leave-it settlement"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 715220.0,
      "end_time": 717436.0,
      "text": "and starting their lives elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 717460.0,
      "end_time": 718676.0,
      "text": "And one can understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 718700.0,
      "end_time": 721676.0,
      "text": "why the company would wish to silence a squeaky wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 721700.0,
      "end_time": 725476.0,
      "text": "What I want to point the finger at is the legal and regulatory system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 725500.0,
      "end_time": 727956.0,
      "text": "a system in which there are networks of agreements"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 727980.0,
      "end_time": 729876.0,
      "text": "just like this one"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 729900.0,
      "end_time": 733459.0,
      "text": "which serve to silence people and seal off data points"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 734380.0,
      "end_time": 737360.0,
      "text": "from public health experts and epidemiologists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 737600.0,
      "end_time": 738675.0,
      "text": "a system in which regulators"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 738700.0,
      "end_time": 741836.0,
      "text": "will even refrain from issuing a violation notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 741860.0,
      "end_time": 743236.0,
      "text": "in the event of pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 743260.0,
      "end_time": 745396.0,
      "text": "if the landowner and the gas company"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 745420.0,
      "end_time": 746996.0,
      "text": "agree to settle."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 747200.0,
      "end_time": 750956.0,
      "text": "This is a system which isn&#39;t just bad from a public health point of view;"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 750980.0,
      "end_time": 754276.0,
      "text": "it exposes hazards to local families"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 754300.0,
      "end_time": 756500.0,
      "text": "who remain in the dark."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 759200.0,
      "end_time": 763516.0,
      "text": "Now, I have given you two examples not because they are isolated examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 763540.0,
      "end_time": 766360.0,
      "text": "They are examples of a systemic problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 766600.0,
      "end_time": 768435.0,
      "text": "I could share some counterexamples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 768460.0,
      "end_time": 771436.0,
      "text": "the case for example of the public official"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 771460.0,
      "end_time": 774556.0,
      "text": "who sues the pharmaceutical company"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 774580.0,
      "end_time": 776196.0,
      "text": "for concealing the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 776220.0,
      "end_time": 782796.0,
      "text": "that its antidepressant increases suicidal thoughts in adolescents."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 782820.0,
      "end_time": 786716.0,
      "text": "I can tell you about the regulator who went after the food company"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 786740.0,
      "end_time": 790476.0,
      "text": "for exaggerating the purported health benefits of its yogurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 790500.0,
      "end_time": 793956.0,
      "text": "And I can tell you about the legislator"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 793980.0,
      "end_time": 798276.0,
      "text": "who despite heavy lobbying directed at both sides of the aisle"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 798300.0,
      "end_time": 802219.0,
      "text": "pushes for environmental protections."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 802980.0,
      "end_time": 804716.0,
      "text": "These are isolated examples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 804740.0,
      "end_time": 808916.0,
      "text": "but they are beacons of light in the darkness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 808940.0,
      "end_time": 812620.0,
      "text": "and they can show us the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 813820.0,
      "end_time": 818100.0,
      "text": "I began by suggesting that sometimes we need to engage in conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 819300.0,
      "end_time": 822835.0,
      "text": "Governments should tussle with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 822860.0,
      "end_time": 828660.0,
      "text": "struggle with, at times engage in direct conflict with corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 829780.0,
      "end_time": 834360.0,
      "text": "This is not because governments are inherently good"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 834600.0,
      "end_time": 836315.0,
      "text": "and corporations are inherently evil."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 836340.0,
      "end_time": 840340.0,
      "text": "Each is capable of good or ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 841260.0,
      "end_time": 845980.0,
      "text": "But corporations understandably act to promote their commercial interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 846900.0,
      "end_time": 852956.0,
      "text": "and they do so either sometimes undermining or promoting the common good."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 852980.0,
      "end_time": 856956.0,
      "text": "But it is the responsibility of governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 856980.0,
      "end_time": 860196.0,
      "text": "to protect and promote the common good."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 860220.0,
      "end_time": 862916.0,
      "text": "And we should insist"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 862940.0,
      "end_time": 865340.0,
      "text": "that they fight to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 866620.0,
      "end_time": 869116.0,
      "text": "This is because governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 869140.0,
      "end_time": 870540.0,
      "text": "are the guardians"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 871420.0,
      "end_time": 872620.0,
      "text": "of public health;"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 873740.0,
      "end_time": 876476.0,
      "text": "governments are the guardians"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 876500.0,
      "end_time": 878356.0,
      "text": "of the environment;"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 878380.0,
      "end_time": 880196.0,
      "text": "and it is governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 880220.0,
      "end_time": 881516.0,
      "text": "that are guardians"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 881540.0,
      "end_time": 886900.0,
      "text": "of these essential parts of our common good."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 887500.0,
      "end_time": 888716.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 888740.0,
      "end_time": 894968.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}